## OmvFeatureFilterDescriptionBuilder.OmvFeatureFilterDescriptionBuilderOptions.processLinesDefault property

If `true`<!-- -->, all unspecified line features will be processed. If `false`<!-- -->, all unspecified line features will be ignored.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
processLinesDefault?: boolean;
```
